{"tid":2448368,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk改咗title","createTime":"2021-03-16T01:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T03:08:21.000Z","uid":89046,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aacc88ff321515b898fe98e1347da5b3d8e8510e","tid":2448368,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:01:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">Technoking of Tesla</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[size=4]Elon Musk Is the New &lsquo;Technoking of Tesla&rsquo; and CFO Is Dubbed &lsquo;Master of Coin&rsquo;[/size=5]</strong><br />\nThe chief executive will retain his role while changing his title at the electric-vehicle maker<br />\n<ins>The change in Mr. Musk&rsquo;s title was disclosed by Tesla in a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission Monday.</ins><br />\n<br />\nBy Matt Grossman<br />\nUpdated March 15, 2021 12:01 pm ET<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/elon-musk-gets-new-title-of-technoking-of-tesla-11615813693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Felon-musk-gets-new-title-of-technoking-of-tesla-11615813693&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirIGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=683e9bce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/elon-musk-gets-new-title-of-technoking-of-tesla-11615813693</a><br />\n<br />\nTesla Inc. said Chief Executive Elon Musk has changed his title at the company to &ldquo;Technoking of Tesla,&rdquo; extending an irreverent streak in the 49-year-old&rsquo;s leadership of the electric-vehicle maker.<br />\n<br />\n<ins>The company also said Chief Financial Officer Zach Kirkhorn will have the title of &ldquo;Master of Coin.&rdquo;</ins> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Both Mr. Musk and Mr. Kirkhorn will maintain their respective positions as CEO and financial chief, according to a regulatory filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission on Monday.<br />\n<br />\nThe company didn&rsquo;t explain the meaning of the titles and didn&rsquo;t respond to an inquiry. Mr. Kirkhorn&rsquo;s new title might carry echoes of Tesla&rsquo;s ambitions around cryptocurrency. Earlier this year, Tesla said that it had invested $1.5 billion in bitcoin and that it aims to start accepting bitcoin as payment from car buyers.<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\nMost job titles for corporate leaders conform to a narrow set of variations, but some Silicon Valley companies have previously used fanciful language to describe workers&rsquo; roles. For years, some companies have used terms such as &ldquo;guru,&rdquo; &ldquo;jedi&rdquo; or &ldquo;ninja&rdquo; to color job descriptions that involve expertise or mental agility. Other colorful titles to emerge include chief happiness officer, chief futurist and chief digital evangelist.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd9523e6c1b82f0f0e7ab1621e8658374772c87","tid":2448368,"uid":384534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:10:13.000Z","msg":"WOW"},{"pid":"fae2437e9a702df7042f1ae595d5d03ce2b8c111","tid":2448368,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:10:21.000Z","msg":"封王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a4b9a0415415b4e423fd01540eaa8e850737a9","tid":2448368,"uid":62850,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:12:41.000Z","msg":"Coin master <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b78d30fb33320be6932ab91c6124ff8efc6f660","tid":2448368,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20